T1  - Note—A Comment on “Modeling the Marketing Mix Decision for Industrial Products”
AU  - Farris, Paul W.
AU  - Buzzell, Robert D.
Y1  - 1980/01/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.26.1.97
